    "title": "Patanjali Ayurved is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Senior)",
    "description": "Patanjali Ayurved has an exciting opening for a Quality Control Engineer at our Chandigarh office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Patanjali Ayurved:\nPatanjali Ayurved is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chandigarh, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Patanjali Ayurved!",
